Changes
=======

v4.0.1 19 Apr 2026
  * Auto-fix jwk.Import / jwk.Export / jwk.FromRaw call sites.
  * Auto-fix obj.Get(name, &dst) -> dst, err := pkg.Get[T](obj, name).
  * Rewrite github.com/lestrrat-go/jwx/v3 -> v4 in go.mod on -fix, then run
    `go mod tidy`.
  * Major scanner speedup on large consumers via narrowed packages.Load,
    per-module parallelism, and a per-batch typed-parse cache.

v4.0.0 19 Apr 2026
  * Initial release. Migration tool and machine-readable rules for moving
    code from github.com/lestrrat-go/jwx/v3 (and v2) to v4.
